    @ControlType(value=javafx.scene.control.MenuItem.class)
@MethodProperties(value={"getId","getStyle","getText","getUserData"})
public class MenuItemWrap<ITEM extends javafx.scene.control.MenuItem>
extends org.jemmy.control.Wrap<ITEM>
    This represents a single menu item within menu hierarchy. It could be looked up starting from a menu bar, a menu button or a context menu.
